                                                                }
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "box": {
                                                                    "fontname": "Arial Italic",
                                                                    "fontsize": 11.0,
                                                                    "id": "obj-87",
                                                                    "linecount": 8,
                                                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                                                    "patching_rect": [
                                                                        512.0,
                                                                        368.0,
                                                                        336.0,
                                                                        105.0
                                                                    ],
                                                                    "text": "What we've really created is a kind of custom metronome. But why wouldn't we want to use a simple metro object and counter to do the same thing? Since we're using an ABSOLUTE position value from the host as an input to calculate WHEN triggers should occur, we ensure that the next pulse will happen at the right time wherever we place our cursor in Live's timeline. We also ensure that the cycle value is \"right\" and that the accent note will occur at the right time in the sequence."
                                                                }
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "box": {
                                                                    "fontname": "Arial Italic",
                                                                    "fontsize": 11.0,
                                                                    "id": "obj-86",
                                                                    "linecount": 12,
                                                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                                                    "patching_rect": [
                                                                        512.0,
                                                                        200.0,
                                                                        322.0,
                                                                        154.0
                                                                    ],
                                                                    "text": "The technique used in this patch involves capturing the current position of the Live application's transport and to match it with a set of specified position values to produce triggers when the transport reaches those positions. The transport position is divided by the <rate> value, and the result is a multiple of <rate>. We can determine what the remainder of each multiple is within a given cycle - how many times the multiple value is contained within the cycle. Whenever that remainder changes, we produce a trigger that becomes the base pulse. Whenever the remainder value is zero, we produce another trigger that's interpreted as an accent. For each remainder value which is not equal to zero, we produce another \"normal note\" trigger."
                                                                }
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "box": {
                                                                    "fontname": "Arial Bold Italic",
                                                                    "fontsize": 11.0,
                                                                    "id": "obj-85",
                                                                    "linecount": 4,
                                                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                                                    "patching_rect": [
                                                                        512.0,
                                                                        136.0,
                                                                        331.0,
                                                                        56.0
                                                                    ],
                                                                    "text": "Goals :\n- create a pulse at a given rate\n- determine accent notes from a given cycle\n- sync the pulse and cycle to Live's transport position"
                                                                }
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "box": {
                                                                    "fontname": "Arial Bold Italic",
                                                                    "fontsize": 14.0,
